msgid ""
"Asymmetric East vs. West variant which pits the western Chess army against a"
" Xiangqi and Janggi-styled army."
msgstr ""
"Asymmetrische \"Osten vs. Westen\" Variante wo sich eine Schach Armee einer "
"Armee im Stil von Xiangqi/Janggi stellt."

#: ../client/i18n.ts:166
msgid ""
"Asymmetric variant which pits the western Chess army against a drop-based, "
"Shogi-styled army."
msgstr ""
"Asymmetrische Variante wo sich eine Schach Armee, einer Armee mit Einsetzen "
"im Stil von Shogi stellt."

